TeacherUnits:
	UNIT Teacher Veteran 0x40 Level(10,Ally,False)     [18,2] 0b 0x0 0x1 REDA16R2 [IronLance, SteelBlade] [0x0,0x0,0x0,0x0]
	UNIT Storm Myrmidon 0x40 Level(10,Ally,False)     [18,3] 0b 0x0 0x1 REDA17R3 [IronLance, SteelBlade] [0x0,0x0,0x0,0x0]
	UNIT Gale Troubadour 0x40 Level(10,Ally,False)     [18,2] 0b 0x0 0x1 REDA18R2 [IronLance, SteelBlade] [0x0,0x0,0x0,0x0]
